author: rhuijben
msg: Following up on r1394748, apply some correctness and performance tweaks.
(svn_client_add4): Check working copy root using a function that doesn't
handle switched paths as a working copy root. Handle 'modern' error codes
like the original function did. As this function just uses the wc_db node
cache for its result we can just call it on a file without a performance
penalty. Use wcroot result to avoid add parents check.
